coffe_detail: Rich, full-bodied espresso in steamed milk, lightly topped with foam. A caffè latte is simply a shot or two of bold, tasty espresso with fresh, sweet steamed milk over it.
Espresso with steamed milk, topped with a deep layer of foam.
Espresso with bittersweet mocha sauce and steamed milk, topped with sweetened whipped cream. Delightful.
Espresso combined with vanilla-flavoured syrup, milk and caramel sauce over ice. A Starbucks classic, chilled for a classic summer’s day.
Just before serving, our slow-steeped Cold Brew is topped with a delicate float of house-made vanilla sweet cream that cascades throughout the cup.
Slow-steeped, small-batch and super smooth. To create our signature recipe, our team spent months experimenting with different brew times and coffee varietals.
A tropical mango and passionfruit infusion, perfectly blended with a fruity hibiscus tea and ice.
Made with freshly brewed Teavana® tea, blended juice and ice.
The Coffee is blended with nonfat milk and ice for a sip on the light side.
Mocha sauce, Frappuccino® roast coffee, milk and ice all come together for a mocha flavor that'll leave you wanting more.
